Reviewed the implementation in `crates/transit-client/src/projection.rs`, `crates/transit-client/src/client.rs`, and `crates/transit-core/src/server.rs`. The new surface stays generic and replay-driven:

- consumers provide their own reducer and view type through `ProjectionReadConsumer`
- the client derives the current view by replaying ordinary hosted `read(...)` records
- the server protocol stays unchanged apart from a generic `RemoteAcknowledged::map_body(...)` helper

No projection-specific schema was hardcoded into Transit core, and no projection-only server truth path was introduced.
